nodes.text: Star Wars: Episode I Mask Punch-Out Book

Star Wars: Episode I Mask Punch-Out Book is a Random House Punch & Play Book with seven punch-out masks of characters from the film Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace: Darth Maul, Jar Jar Binks, Queen Amidala, Qui-Gon Jinn, Obi-Wan Kenobi, Anakin Skywalker, and Yoda. The book was released on August 17, 1999 with mask illustrations provided by the Thompson Brothers. Each mask page features a film quote to accompany the illustrated character.
